Lucide icon subset for Zenith native icon presets.

Source project: Lucide
Homepage: https://lucide.dev/
Repository: https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide
License: ISC License

The SVG files in this directory are a checked-in subset adapted from Lucide icons for the embedded @zenith/icons-lucide library pack.

The SVG files are whitespace-normalized copies of the upstream Lucide SVGs (each collapsed to a single line); the vector geometry is unmodified. The exact upstream revision (tag/commit) they were vendored from was not recorded at vendoring time.

Three local file names are legacy/renamed aliases that differ from the current upstream icon names:

  sync           = upstream refresh-cw
  upload-cloud   = upstream cloud-upload
  download-cloud = upstream cloud-download

A machine-readable manifest of these mappings, together with the SHA-256 of every vendored SVG, is recorded alongside this file in provenance.json.

